- 想做一个
	- 向上翻的手机网页
	- 怎么问ai好呢？

### 提问

```
我想制作一个手机网页文件html，文件中总共三个页面，背景分别为红绿蓝，每个页面都是全屏显示，红色显示时，其他页面不显示。支持触控，触控初始位置-触控结束位置大于30px时，完成翻页功能。
```

- ai理解了
	- 给了我三个文件

![图片描述](data:image/png;base64,) 

### 合并请求

![图片描述](data:image/png;base64,) 

- 得到代码

```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>全屏翻页</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body, html {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .page {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: none;
        }

        .red {
            background-color: red;
        }

        .green {
            background-color: green;
        }

        .blue {
            background-color: blue;
        }

        #redPage {
            display: block; /* 初始显示红色页面 */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page red" id="redPage"></div>
    <div class="page green" id="greenPage"></div>
    <div class="page blue" id="bluePage"></div>

    <script>
        let currentPage = 0; // 当前显示的页面索引
        const pages = document.querySelectorAll('.page');
        const totalPages = pages.length;

        function showPage(index) {
            for (let i = 0; i < totalPages; i++) {
                pages[i].style.display = 'none';
            }
            if (index >= 0 && index < totalPages) {
                pages[index].style.display = 'block';
            }
        }

        let startX, startY, endX, endY;

        document.addEventListener('touchstart', function(event) {
            startX = event.touches[0].clientX;
            startY = event.touches[0].clientY;
        });

        document.addEventListener('touchend', function(event) {
            endX = event.changedTouches[0].clientX;
            endY = event.changedTouches[0].clientY;

            const deltaX = endX - startX;
            const deltaY = endY - startY;

            if (Math.abs(deltaX) > 30) {
                if (deltaX > 0) {
                    // 向右滑动，显示上一个页面
                    currentPage = (currentPage - 1 + totalPages) % totalPages;
                } else {
                    // 向左滑动，显示下一个页面
                    currentPage = (currentPage + 1) % totalPages;
                }
                showPage(currentPage);
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```

### 最新代码

![图片描述](data:image/png;base64,) 

```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>全屏翻页</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body, html {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .page {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            display: none;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 6vw; /* 超大字体 */
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .red {
            background-color: red;
        }

        .green {
            background-color: green;
        }

        .blue {
            background-color: blue;
        }

        #redPage {
            display: flex; /* 初始显示红色页面 */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page red" id="redPage">
        <div id="pageIndex0">0</div>
    </div>
    <div class="page green" id="greenPage">
        <div id="pageIndex1">1</div>
    </div>
    <div class="page blue" id="bluePage">
        <div id="pageIndex2">2</div>
    </div>

    <script>
        let currentPage = 0; // 当前显示的页面索引
        const pages = document.querySelectorAll('.page');
        const totalPages = pages.length;

        function showPage(index) {
            for (let i = 0; i < totalPages; i++) {
                pages[i].style.display = 'none';
            }
            if (index >= 0 && index < totalPages) {
                pages[index].style.display = 'flex';
                // 更新页面中的索引值
                pages[index].querySelector('div').textContent = index;
            }
        }

        let startY, endY;

        document.addEventListener('touchstart', function(event) {
            startY = event.touches[0].clientY;
        });

        document.addEventListener('touchend', function(event) {
            endY = event.changedTouches[0].clientY;

            const deltaY = startY - endY; // 注意这里是 startY - endY

            if (Math.abs(deltaY) > 30) {
                if (deltaY > 0) {
                    // 向上滑动，显示下一个页面
                    currentPage = (currentPage + 1) % totalPages;
                } else {
                    // 向下滑动，显示上一个页面
                    currentPage = (currentPage - 1 + totalPages) % totalPages;
                }
                showPage(currentPage);
            }
        });

        // 初始化显示第一个页面
        showPage(currentPage);
    </script>
</body>
</html>
```
